feat: adopt SWR for trending pages with server-side pagination

- Add SWR dependency and shared hooks infrastructure:
  - lib/swr/fetcher.ts: generic JSON fetcher + URL builder
  - lib/swr/useTrending.ts: typed hooks for videos/products/creators
  - lib/swr/useCategories.ts: cached categories hook (10min dedup)

- Add server-side pagination to all trending API routes:
  - Replace limit param with page + pageSize (max 100)
  - Add Prisma count() for total, skip/take for pagination
  - Response includes total, page, pageSize, hasMore

- Migrate all 3 trending pages from manual fetch to SWR:
  - Videos: useTrendingVideos + useCategories, client-side category filter
  - Products: useTrendingProducts + useCategories, client-side category filter
  - Creators: useTrendingCreators, simplified (no categories)
  - Remove ~15 manual useState/useEffect/useCallback per page
  - 30s dedup prevents redundant API calls
  - keepPreviousData avoids flash on filter change

All 292 tests passing.
